creator: Candidly Android
descriptionHtml:
LET YOUR PROGRAMMING SKILLS CREATE JOB OPPORTUNITIES

CANDIDLY matches you to employers based solely on your software skills. Our skills-based approach gives every capable candidate equal access to employment opportunities, regardless of background, experience, education, disability, race, age or gender.


We make it simple and easy for you to be made visible to employers in search of your skills:

 • Build your résumé of skills – Complete your profile to ensure that employers are able to easily identify you for job opportunities that require your skills.
 • Create confidence in your skills - Take our bite-sized mobile challenges in your chosen skill, and increase your skill accuracy. The better your accuracy, the higher your profile is ranked in employer searches.
 • Be invited to apply – You create job opportunities through your resume of skills, allowing
 • Develop yourself – Use our personalized feedback to understand which skills are in demand and how you compare to your peers, create more opportunities by improving on your skillset.
descriptionShort: Create job opportunities using your software skills

descriptionHtml:

Employers find you

Complete your anonymous profile to ensure that Employers are able to easily identify you for job opportunities based on your programming skills.

2. Verify your skills
Taking our custom-built programming skill challenges will increase our confidence in your capability, and rank you higher when an Employer searches for your skills.

3. Be invited to apply for jobs
Employers find you based on your programming skills, and can immediately invite you to apply for positions.

4. Attract more opportunities
Use our personalized feedback to understand which skills are in demand, and how you can develop your skillset to stand out from your peers.

We’re always excited to hear from you! If you have any feedback, questions or concerns, please reach out to us at info@candidly.me.

title: Candidly

creator: Candidly Android
descriptionHtml:
Our skills-first approach levels the playing field by removing bias from the employer screening process – giving you more access to opportunities.

YOU’RE ELIGIBLE FOR ROLES AS SOON AS YOUR PROFILE IS CREATED!

One profile for all jobs
Build a single skills profile that is automatically matched to every open role that requires your skills.

Receive equal opportunity
Anonymous profiles ensure you’re only matched to jobs based on your programming skills.

Employers find you
Interested employers reach out to you, giving you more confidence that you will be considered for the role.

WE MAKE IT EASY FOR YOU TO SHOWCASE YOUR PROGRAMMING SKILLS TO ATTRACT EMPLOYERS LOOKING TO HIRE

1. Create your skills profile
Simply select your programming skills and level of proficiency.

2. Verify your skills
Take short multiple-choice challenges to build confidence and wow employers with your skills.

3. Attract job opportunities
Employers interested in your skills invite you to submit your resume for open roles.

4. Only be considered for the roles you want
Your profile remains completely anonymous until you’ve accepted the resume request.

We’re always excited to hear from you! If you have any feedback, questions or concerns, please reach out to us at info@candidly.me.

title: Candidly

creator: Candidly Android
descriptionHtml:
Do you find it painful applying for jobs? It doesn’t have to be. Candidly makes it easy for you to find the Software Developer job you want by automatically matching you to roles based solely on your programming skills.

How does it work? It’s simple:
• Create your skills profile and indicate your role preferences.
• Get immediately notified of available roles you’re a match for.
• Apply only to those roles you’re interested in.
• We send your application to the recruiter for review.
• Receive guaranteed feedback, regardless of the outcome.

Our commitment to you
• You are only notified of the jobs that you want to see.
• You are never overlooked for a job you have the skills for.
• You only need one resume for all applications.
• You receive meaningful and relevant feedback on every application.

We give you a fair chance
We use your programming skills to not only match you to roles, but to demonstrate your suitability to recruiters. Your Candidly profile is completely anonymous, ensuring you are initially considered for the role based solely on your programming skills.

We’re always excited to hear from you! If you have any feedback, questions or concerns, please reach out to us at info@candidly.me.
